Two <i>chukadon</i> and two <i>gyoza</i>.

63
00:04:02,942 --> 00:04:08,648
<i>Now 50 years old, this is his first time
as the main character in a drama series.</i>

64
00:04:09,816 --> 00:04:11,217
Show me.

65
