Papa, he's hiding something.
I just know it!

68
00:04:18,424 --> 00:04:20,860
-Oh, oh, oh!
-What? What are you doing?

69
00:04:20,927 --> 00:04:22,962
-Ohhh!
-Ouch...

70
00:04:23,029 --> 00:04:24,664
Let me go already.

71
00:04:24,731 --> 00:04:27,000
Have you been properly resting?

72
00:04:27,066 --> 00:04:30,903
Of course, I want to.
But I need time to read the lines.

73
00:04:30,970 --> 00:04:32,505
I have to remember them.

74
